><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">片[<span style="color:#000099;">piàn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- thin piece<br>- flake<br>- a slice<br>- film<br>- TV play<br>- to slice<br>- to carve thin<br>- partial<br>- incomplete<br>- one-sided<br>- classifier for slices, tablets, tract of land, area of water<br>- classifier for CDs, movies, DVDs etc<br>- used with numeral <a href="/dictionary/一">一</a>[yi1]: classifier for scenario, scene, feeling, atmosphere, sound etc<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+7247</p></div>

